<feed xml:lang="en" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><title>边缘 - 所有帖子</title><icon>https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/community_logos/52801/VER_Logomark_32x32..png</icon><updated> 2023-12-19T20:36:57-05:00</updated><id> https://www.theverge.com/rss/full.xml</id><link href="https://www.theverge.com/" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><entry><published> 2023-12-19T20:36:57-05:00</published><updated> 2023-12-19T20:36:57-05:00</updated><title> The Verge 2023 年最受欢迎的值得挥霍的礼物</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;各种产品的照片插图，背景为明亮的星星图形。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/LeMh_lYwSS716rkGuwdzNMqNLuA=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72937150/236830_WORTH_THE_SPLURGE_Gift_Guide _Art_CVirginia_LEDE_2040x1360.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;照片插图由 Amelia Holowaty Krales 和 Cath Virginia / The Verge 拍摄&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;当金钱不再是问题时，天空就是极限，所以为什么要将辛苦赚来的现金和硬币浪费在日常必需品上？是时候实现远大梦想了。&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23920823/expense-holiday-gifts-wishes-extravagant-ideas-presents-2023&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip; &lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/23920823/expensive-holiday-gifts-wishes-extravagant-ideas-presents-2023" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/23920823/expense-holiday-gifts-wishes-extravagant-ideas-presents-2023</id><author><name>边缘人员</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-12-19T19:21:31-05:00</published><updated> 2023-12-19T19:21:31-05:00</updated><title> The Verge 2023 年游戏和娱乐节日礼物指南</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;照片插图，手拿着各种产品，背景是明亮的星星。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/Oziq9Th2P1ckSgzRT0ZYrugXX8Y=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72871362/236830_GAME_AND_ENT_2_Gift_Guide_Artboards_ CVirginia_LEDE_2040x1360.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;照片插图由 Amelia Holowaty Krales 和 Cath Virginia / The Verge 拍摄&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;即使有人喜欢购买所有最新的大型游戏，我们也确信我们可以帮助您找到它们这个节日的独特且足够极客的礼物。&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23959483/gaming-entertainment-gifts-ideas-2023-playstation-nintendo-xbox-tv -accessories&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/23959483/gaming-entertainment-gifts-ideas-2023-playstation-nintendo-xbox-tv-accessories" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/23959483/gaming-entertainment-gifts-ideas-2023-playstation-nintendo-xbox-tv-accessories</id><author><name>安东尼奥·G·迪·贝内代托</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-12-19T19:09:17-05:00</published><updated> 2023-12-19T19:09:17-05:00</updated><title> Rite Aid 因“鲁莽”使用而被禁止面部识别五年</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;店面显示 Rite Aid 徽标的照片&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/AeTWd__w34__8LukewcEYZ8OAxE=/0x2:5000x3335/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn。 com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72980735/1258931679.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;图片：Getty&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;tDYeoq&quot;>;Rite Aid 不允许使用人工智能面部护理作为 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.ftc.gov/news-events/news/press-releases/2023/12/rite-aid-banned-using-ai-facial- 的一部分，识别技术再延长五年recognize-after-ftc-says-retailer-deployed-technology-without?utm_campaign=rite_aid_banned_from_usin&amp;amp;utm_content=1703022035&amp;amp;utm_medium=social&amp;amp;utm_source=twitter&quot;>;与联邦贸易委员会达成和解&lt;/a>;。在&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.ftc.gov/system/files/ftc_gov/pdf/2023190_riteaid_complaint_filed.pdf&quot;>;周二提交的一份投诉&lt;/a>;中，FTC 指控 Rite Aid 在从 2012 年到 2020 年，这种行为“鲁莽”。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;ZmAQEx&quot;>;联邦贸易委员会表示，在此期间，Rite Aid 使用面部识别技术“捕获所有进入或穿过商店的消费者的图像” ”。据称，该公司随后创建了一个数据库，其中包含被识别为入店行窃者或表现出其他可疑行为的客户。对于某些顾客来说，数据库会包含“附带信息”，例如姓名、出生日期以及商店认为可疑的活动……&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www. theverge.com/2023/12/19/24008516/rite-aid-facial-recognition-ban-ftc- Five-years&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2023/12/19/24008516/rite-aid-facial-recognition-ban-ftc-five-years" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2023/12/19/24008516/rite-aid-facial-recognition-ban-ftc- Five-years</id><author><name>艾玛·罗斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-12-19T18:55:16-05:00</published><updated> 2023-12-19T18:55:16-05:00</updated><title> Epic不会禁止仅限成人分级的区块链游戏</title><content type="html">&lt;图>; &lt;img alt=&quot;Epic Games 徽标&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/fE6sbLLp1sYsKePh31drYRi8o54=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/ image/72980707/acastro_STK108__01.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;由 Alex Castro / The Verge 绘制的插图&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;UJCSlV&quot;>;区块链游戏正在重返 Epic Games 市场。 Epic Games Store 严格禁止被娱乐软件评级委员会 (ESRB) 归类为“仅限成人”的游戏——通常是过度裸露或暴力的游戏。但市场今天&lt;a href=&quot;https://t.co/RQGGzWGeG8&quot;>;宣布&lt;/a>;，区块链游戏被归类为 AO &lt;em>;仅仅是因为&lt;/em>;它们使用区块链，这是此规则的例外。 &lt;/p>; &lt;div id=&quot;ld6s0b&quot;>; &lt;blockquote class=&quot;twitter-tweet&quot;>; &lt;p lang=&quot;en&quot; dir=&quot;ltr&quot;>; 注意：Gods Unchained 和 Striker Manager 3 已于我们对基于区块链的游戏评级的内容政策进行了更改。了解更多信息：&lt;a href=&quot;https://t.co/RQGGzWGeG8&quot;>;https://t.co/RQGGzWGeG8&lt;/a>;&lt;/p>;— Epic Games Store (@EpicGames) &lt;a href=&quot;https ://twitter.com/EpicGames/status/1737200788622225625?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw&quot;>;2023 年 12 月 19 日&lt;/a>; &lt;/blockquote>; &lt;/div>; &lt;p id=&quot;4a5mVV&quot;>;“一些基于区块链的游戏正在接受行业评级机构针对其特定内容的仅限成人 (AO) 评级&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/12/19/24008602/epic- games-store-adults-only-blockchain-games&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2023/12/19/24008602/epic-games-store-adults-only-blockchain-games" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2023/12/19/24008602/epic-games-store-adults-only-blockchain-games</id><author><name>阿姆丽塔·哈立德</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-12-19T18:38:19-05:00</published><updated> 2023-12-19T18:38:19-05:00</updated><title> The Verge 2023 年家居科技节日礼物指南</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;手拿着不同的产品，背景是色彩鲜艳的星星。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/E-LpdUcMKJSz2TPCi6T59dz2TjI=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72842014/236830_HOME_TECH_Gift_Guide_Artboards_CV irginia_LEDE_2040x1360.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;照片插图由 Amelia Holowaty Krales 和 Cath Virginia / The Verge 拍摄&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;从变色灯到为您和您的宠物准备晚餐的小工具，这里有一些我们最喜欢的智能家居礼物。&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23933231/smart-home-tech-gift-guide-2023-video-doorbells-plugs-机器人吸尘器&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/23933231/smart-home-tech-gift-guide-2023-video-doorbells-plugs-robot-vacuums" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/23933231/smart-home-tech-gift-guide-2023-video-doorbells-plugs-robot-vacuums</id><author><name>希娜·瓦萨尼</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-12-19T18:35:47-05:00</published><updated> 2023-12-19T18:35:47-05:00</updated><title> FBI 取缔后勒索软件团伙“夺取”其网站并发出新威胁</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;卡通插图显示一个阴影人物拿着一个红色目录文件夹，文件夹的侧面有一张惊讶的脸。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/TyuvsoYQ2yezkG_LZIchtSqYfuU=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72980665/VRG_Illo_STK001_B_Sala_Hacker.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;插图：Beatrice Sala&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;DrwYiD&quot;>;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.justice.gov/opa/pr/justice-department-disrupts-prolific -alphvblackcat-ransomware-variant&quot;>;美国司法部 (DOJ) 表示&lt;/a>;，作为跨国执法行动的一部分，FBI 已创建了一款解密工具，帮助其返回 500 多名勒索软件受害者的数据。它还写道，该局查获了由 ALPHV / Blackcat 勒索软件团伙运营的“几个网站”。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;8iUUQ0&quot;>;但是，&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.bleepingcomputer.com/ news/security/fbi-disrupts-blackcat-ransomware-operation-creates-decryption-tool/&quot;>;&lt;em>;电脑发出响声&lt;/em>;报告&lt;/a>;，截至今天下午，ALPHV / Blackcat 声称已重新控制其网站，FBI 仅拥有 400 家左右公司的解密密钥，导致 3,000 多名受害者的数据仍处于加密状态。据报道，该团伙还表示，不再限制分支机构使用其勒索软件攻击关键基础设施，包括医院和核电站。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;CQSP0G&quot;>;据...&lt;/p>; &lt;p >; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/12/19/24008093/alphv-blackcat-ransomware-gang-site-seized-fbi-doj&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/ p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2023/12/19/24008093/alphv-blackcat-ransomware-gang-site-seized-fbi-doj" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2023/12/19/24008093/alphv-blackcat-ransomware-gang-site-seized-fbi-doj</id><author><name>韦斯·戴维斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-12-19T17:51:52-05:00</published><updated> 2023-12-19T17:51:52-05:00</updated><title> The Verge 2023 年 PC 礼品指南</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;照片插图，手拿着各种产品，背景是明亮的星星图形背景。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/NKp7YtAgU_mcPIzB9I2SJBfnyLU=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72825088/236830_PC_Gift_Guide_Art_CVirginia_LEDE _2040x1360.0.jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;照片插图由 Amelia Holowaty Krales 和 Cath Virginia / The Verge 拍摄&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;对于那些花太多时间坐在笔记本电脑或台式电脑上的人来说，这是最好的科技礼物——无论是工作还是工作休闲。&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23919557/holiday-gift-ideas-2023-pc-desktop-laptop-wfh-content-creator-tech-gadgets&quot; >;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/23919557/holiday-gift-ideas-2023-pc-desktop-laptop-wfh-content-creator-tech-gadgets" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/23919557/holiday-gift-ideas-2023-pc-desktop-laptop-wfh-content-creator-tech-gadgets</id><author><name>安东尼奥·G·迪·贝内代托</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-12-19T17:29:57-05:00</published><updated> 2023-12-19T17:29:57-05:00</updated><title>苹果的 iPhone 卫星系统为路边援助提供了新选项</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;照片显示用户成功连接到范围内的卫星。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/TD5IlNZoDBV6H77OyPswizhZmxE=/0x390:1125x1140/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72980452/IMG_0384.0.jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;摄影：Victoria Song / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;5xFYwf&quot;>;如果您拥有 iPhone 14 或 iPhone 15，您现在可以使用卫星连接访问 Verizon 的路边援助服务。在&lt;a href=&quot;https://support.apple.com/en-us/105098&quot;>;支持页面&lt;/a>;中&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.macrumors.com/2023/12/19 /verizon-roadside-assistance-apple-satellite/&quot;>;MacRumors 发现，Apple 现在表示您可以在运行 iOS 17.2（或更高版本）和 Verizon 的设备上利用该功能SIM 卡。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;Si16ez&quot;>;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.anrdoezrs.net/links/8532386/type/dlg/sid/verge/https://www.verizon。 com/solutions-and-services/add-ons/safety/roadside-assistance?cjdata=MXxOfDB8WXww&amp;amp;URL=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.verizon.com%2Fsolutions-and-services%2Fadd-ons%2Fsafety%2Froadside-援助&amp;CMP=afc_h_p_cj_oth_fios_2022_04&amp;amp;SID=73726X1523000X36f0f597c3d5345bd2380d3050ee18aa&amp;cjevent=77b905989ead11ee832200e30a82b82c&amp;amp;vendorid=C JM&amp;PID=100045529&amp;amp;AID=11557999#overview&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;Verizon 的路边援助计划&lt;/a>;由 Allstate 旗下的 Signature Motor Club 运营，在您遇到汽车故障时提供帮助，即使您开的是朋友的车或租来的车。它包括向任何方向拖曳车辆长达 10 英里、绞车、燃油输送、跨接启动、轮胎服务等。虽然 Verizon 提供每条线路每月 4.99 美元的订阅费，但它还 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.anrdoezrs.net/links/8532386/type/dlg/sid/verge/https://www.verizon.com/support /roadside-assistance-faqs/&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;为未订阅而使用该服务的 Verizon 客户提供固定费用&lt;/a>;。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;NbyJmb&quot; >;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/9/12/23870328/apple-iphone-roadside-assistance-emergency-sos-satellite-aaa&quot;>;一个...&lt;/a>;&lt; /p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/12/19/24008362/apple-iphone-verizon-roadside-assistance-satellite&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt; /p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2023/12/19/24008362/apple-iphone-verizon-roadside-assistance-satellite" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2023/12/19/24008362/apple-iphone-verizon-roadside-assistance-satellite</id><author><name>艾玛·罗斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-12-19T17:24:58-05:00</published><updated> 2023-12-19T17:24:58-05:00</updated><title>大众、保时捷和奥迪最终表示将使用特斯拉的电动汽车充电插头</title><content type="html">&lt;图>; &lt;img alt=&quot;大众电动汽车使用特斯拉超级充电站充电&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/nuAQsGCWmNaZVc-wbuEzW0WpjL4=/0x224:1000x891/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn. com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72980440/17363_VolkswagenAudiPorscheandScoutMotorsbrandstoimplementtheNorthAmericanChargingStandardinfutureelectricvehicles.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;图片：大众&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;W87Kg9&quot;>;大众集团，还拥有奥迪、保时捷、和 Scout Motors 终于做了几乎所有其他汽车制造商已经做过的事情：宣布打算采用特斯拉的电动汽车充电标准。 &lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;6MjRHG&quot;>;大众表示正在“探索适配器解决方案”，以便其当前的电动汽车车主可以访问特斯拉的超级充电网络，并预计到 2025 年推出一些东西。同年，您将开始看到配备特斯拉充电端口的新型大众电动汽车下线。总而言之，大众汽车表示，这笔交易将使其客户能够使用北美 15,000 个超级充电站。 &lt;/p>; &lt;div class=&quot;c-float-left c-float-hang&quot;>;&lt;aside id=&quot;V0SwOb&quot;>;&lt;q>;大众表示正在“探索适配器解决方案”&lt;/q>;&lt;/aside>;&lt; /div>; &lt;p id=&quot;QtlUZ3&quot;>;当然，大众在这次游行中来得太晚了。事情开始滚滚而来......&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/12/19/24008426/volkswagen-audi-porsche-tesla-nacs-ev-charging -plug&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2023/12/19/24008426/volkswagen-audi-porsche-tesla-nacs-ev-charging-plug" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2023/12/19/24008426/volkswagen-audi-porsche-tesla-nacs-ev-charging-plug</id><author><name>安德鲁·霍金斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-12-19T16:40:00-05:00</published><updated> 2023-12-19T16:40:00-05:00</updated><title>以下是一些您仍然可以在假期前及时获取的礼物</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;2022 iPad Air&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/bM90KzT_o9xBwPJkK60zaEpsbYU=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image /image/72980278/akrales_220314_5071_0026.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;图片：Amelia Holowaty Krales / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;jXl7CJ&quot;>;12 月已经过去，留给你的时间所剩无几完成你的假期购物？我不是来评判你等到最后一刻的（毕竟我们都经历过）。相反，我会帮助您找到各种礼物创意，这些礼物仍然应该在圣诞节前及时送达并包装好并塞在圣诞树下，从而为您提供更好的帮助。&lt;/p>; &lt;div class=&quot;c-float-left c -float-hang&quot;>;&lt;aside id=&quot;7jzJCw&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem-component=&quot;readmore&quot; data-anthem-component-data=&#39;{&quot;stories&quot;:[{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;The Verge 的 2023 年假期礼物指南&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23939057/holiday-gift-guide-2023-best-ideas-unique-tech-gadgets&quot;},{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;The Verge 的最爱100 美元以下的节日礼物&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23951136/gifts-under-100-best-cheap-tech-ideas-2023-budget&quot;},{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;The Verge 最喜欢的 50 美元以下节日礼物 &quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23952179/tech-gifts-under-50-best-cheap-ideas-2023-budget&quot;},{&quot;title&quot;: &quot;The Verge 最喜欢的 25 美元以下节日礼物&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23874403/tech-gifts-under-25-best-cheap-ideas-stocking-stuffers-2023-budget&quot;} ]}&#39;>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/aside>;&lt;/div>; &lt;p id=&quot;QZ6mka&quot;>;您仍然可以获得大量精美礼品 - 其中一些甚至可能正在打折 - 包括智能家居配件、平板电脑、可穿戴设备和耳机。这里的所有内容都是 The Verge 测试或担保的技术或技术相关内容，因此您可以放心，您不会为了及时性而牺牲质量。如果您需要其他想法，请务必查看...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24005725/best-last- 分钟-christmas-gifts-ideas -tech-wireless-earbuds-laptops-gaming-shipping&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/24005725/best-last-minute-christmas-gifts-ideas-tech-wireless-earbuds-laptops-gaming-shipping" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/24005725/best-last-一分钟-christmas-gifts-ideas-tech-wireless-earbuds-laptops-gaming-shipping</id><author><name>安东尼奥